<div id="review_1996093637" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1996093637" />
    <a title="Chris F" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9582057-chris-f"><img alt="Chris F" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1337234709p2/9582057.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1996093637?book_show_action=true">May 16, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Chris F" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Chris F" href="/user/show/9582057-chris-f">Chris F</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9582057-chris-f?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9582057-chris-f?shelf=favourite-authors">favourite-authors</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9582057-chris-f?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1996093637" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer804323417224833766">I really enjoy this series set in Tibet with a Chinese investigator who used to be a top corruption investigator in Beijing until he fell fowl of the political establishment and spent years in a Chinese gulag in Tibet. Now he has been released but lives just outside the law with a group of illegal Tibetan llamas. Despite this he still manages to solve intricately plotted murders. This one is as well written and entertaining as the others in the series.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


